description: Generates a traffic analysis report for the timeframe and traffic type you specify. For information on the contents of a traffic analysis report, see  AnalysisReport.

parameters.name: FirewallName
parameters.description: The descriptive name of the firewall. You can't change the name of a firewall after you create it. You must specify the ARN or the name, and you can specify both.

parameters.name: FirewallArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the firewall. You must specify the ARN or the name, and you can specify both.

parameters.name: AnalysisType
parameters.description: The type of traffic that will be used to generate a report.

nested_items.name: AnalysisReportId
nested_items.description: The unique ID of the query that ran when you requested an analysis report.
